o relocate failover hardware for the Account Center.\n<br />\n<br /><b>Why is this maintenance happening?</b>\n<br />\n<br />This maintenance is happening because failure of the equipment could cause prolonged downtime. This is being done as preventative maintenance.\n<br />\n<br /><b>Symptoms:</b>\n<br />•  Account Center sessions expiring, you may need to log back in.</p>      \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 27 Oct 2016 21:11:29 -0700\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"http://status.mediatemple.net/incidents/h6vmm4jklhgy\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"http://status.mediatemple.net/incidents/h6vmm4jklhgy\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:40:\"\n      \n      \n      \n      \n      \n    \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25:\"Grid Hardware Maintenance\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1658:\"\n<p><small>Oct 24, 22:57 PDT</small><br><strong>Completed</strong> - Maintenance on Cluster 12 was completed successfully. Cluster 10 will be rescheduled for a later date.</p><p><small>Oct 24, 21:00 PDT</small><br><strong>In progress</strong> - Scheduled maintenance is currently in progress. We will provide updates as necessary.</p><p><small>Oct 24, 20:35 PDT</small><br><strong>Scheduled</strong> - We will be performing a scheduled system maintenance on Monday, October 24, 2016 to our Grid hosting service. Here are the important details:\n<br />\n<br /><b>Who is affected?</b>\n<br />\n<br />This maintenance will affect customers on the following servers:\n<br />\n<br />Cluster 10\n<br />Cluster 12\n<br />\n<br />You may verify whether or not your services are being impacted by this issue by locating your Cluster and Storage Segment in your Server Guide. For more information on how to locate your Server Guide in the AccountCenter, please reference the following (mt) Community article.\n<br />\n<br />Server Guide\n<br />https://mediatemple.net/community/products/grid/204643840/server-guide\n<br />\n<br /><b>When will this maintenance happen?</b>\n<br />\n<br />This maintenance will occur between 9:00 PM and 1:00 AM PT, Monday, October 24, 2016.\n<br />\n<br /><b>What is changing?</b>\n<br />\n<br />This maintenance will consolidate our Grid Cluster hardware.\n<br />\n<br /><b>Why is this maintenance happening?</b>\n<br />\n<br />This maintenance is happening because failure of the equipment could cause prolonged downtime. This is being done as preventative maintenance.\n<br />\n<br /><b>Symptoms:</b>\n<br />•  Inability to access web, SSH, or FTP.</p>      \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 24 Oct 2016 22:57:04 -0700\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"http://status.mediatemple.net/incidents/wxq9fdf3zpj3\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"http://status.mediatemple.net/incidents/wxq9fdf3zpj3\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:40:\"\n      \n      \n      \n      \n      \n    \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25:\"(mt) Hardware Maintenance\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1267:\"\n<p><small>Oct 24, 21:11 PDT</small><br><strong>Completed</strong> - The scheduled maintenance has been completed.</p><p><small>Oct 24, 21:01 PDT</small><br><strong>In progress</strong> - Scheduled maintenance is currently in progress. We will provide updates as necessary.</p><p><small>Oct 24, 19:27 PDT</small><br><strong>Scheduled</strong> - We will be performing scheduled system maintenance on Monday, October 24, 2016. Here are the important details:\n<br />\n<br /><b>Who is affected?</b>\n<br />\n<br />This maintenance will affect customers who are logged into the AccountCenter.  Customers may be logged out of the AccountCenter and will need to log back in.\n<br />\n<br /><b>When will this maintenance happen?</b>\n<br />\n<br />This maintenance will occur between 9:00 PM and 1:00 AM PT, Monday, October 24, 2016.\n<br />\n<br /><b>What is changing?</b>\n<br />\n<br />This maintenance will be performed in preparation for a necessary hardware migration.\n<br />\n<br /><b>Why is this maintenance happening?</b>\n<br />\n<br />This maintenance is happening because failure of the equipment could cause prolonged downtime. This is being done as preventative maintenance.\n<br />\n<br /><b>Symptoms:</b>\n<br />•  Customers may be logged out of the AccountCenter.</p>      \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 24 Oct 2016 21:11:53 -0700\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0