and 1:00 AM PT, Thursday, October 6, 2016.\n<br />\n<br /><b>What is changing?</b>\n<br />\n<br />This maintenance will replace a failed CPU on Cluster 02, Storage Segment 05.\n<br />\n<br /><b>Why is this maintenance happening?</b>\n<br />\n<br />This maintenance is happening because failure of the equipment could cause prolonged downtime. This is being done as preventative maintenance.\n<br />\n<br /><b>Symptoms:</b>\n<br />•  Inability to access web, SSH, or FTP.</p>      \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 06 Oct 2016 21:44:42 -0700\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"http://status.mediatemple.net/incidents/lds2gvb2z3pl\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"http://status.mediatemple.net/incidents/lds2gvb2z3pl\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:17;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:40:\"\n      \n      \n      \n      \n      \n    \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:36:\"Grid Cluster 08 Service Interruption\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1025:\"\n<p><small>Oct  4, 13:49 PDT</small><br><strong>Resolved</strong> - This incident has been resolved.</p><p><small>Oct  4, 13:33 PDT</small><br><strong>Identified</strong> - (mt) Engineers are currently working on an issue affecting web accessibility for customers on Cluster 08 of the Grid.\n<br />\n<br />You may verify whether or not your services are being impacted by this issue by locating your Cluster in your Server Guide. For more information on how to locate your Server Guide in the AccountCenter, please reference the following (mt) Community article.\n<br />\n<br /><a href=\"https://mediatemple.net/community/products/grid/204644050/\">https://mediatemple.net/community/products/grid/204644050/</a>\n<br />\n<br />We are actively working on getting this issue resolved as soon as possible. We sincerely apologize for any inconvenience that this may cause, and we appreciate your patience while we work quickly towards a resolution.\n<br />\n<br /><b>Symptoms:</b>\n<br />•  Inability to access web, FTP, or SSH.</p>      \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 04 Oct 2016 13:49:07 -0700\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"http://status.mediatemple.net/incidents/0v537wh8yxwg\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"http://status.mediatemple.net/incidents/0v537wh8yxwg\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:18;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:40:\"\n      \n      \n      \n      \n      \n    \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25:\"Grid Hardware Maintenance\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1616:\"\n<p><small>Oct  3, 21:25 PDT</small><br><strong>Completed</strong> - The scheduled maintenance has been completed.</p><p><small>Oct  3, 21:00 PDT</small><br><strong>In progress</strong> - Scheduled maintenance is currently in progress. We will provide updates as necessary.</p><p><small>Oct  3, 18:04 PDT</small><br><strong>Scheduled</strong> - We will be performing a scheduled system maintenance on Monday, October 3, 2016 to our Grid hosting service. Here are the important details:\n<br />\n<br /><b>Who is affected?</b>\n<br />\n<br />This maintenance will affect customers on the following servers:\n<br />\n<br />Cluster 01\n<br />\n<br />You may verify whether or not your services are being impacted by this issue by locating your Cluster and Storage Segment in your Server Guide. For more information on how to locate your Server Guide in the AccountCenter, please reference the following (mt) Community article.\n<br />\n<br />Server Guide\n<br />https://mediatemple.net/community/products/grid/204643840/server-guide\n<br />\n<br /><b>When will this maintenance happen?</b>\n<br />\n<br />This maintenance will occur between 9:00 PM and 1:00 AM PT, Monday, October 3, 2016.\n<br />\n<br /><b>What is changing?</b>\n<br />\n<br />This maintenance will make software changes to the hardware on Clusters 01\n<br />\n<br /><b>Why is this maintenance happening?</b>\n<br />\n<br />This maintenance is happening because failure of the equipment could cause prolonged downtime. This is being done to improve security, stability, and performance.\n<br />\n<br /><b>Symptoms:</b>\n<br />•  Inability to access web, SSH, or FTP.</p>      \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 03 Oct 2016 21:25:13 -0700\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"http://status.mediatemple.net/incidents/7ffnh6nvjb1z\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"http://status.mediatemple.net/incidents/7ffnh6nvjb1z\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:19;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:40:\"\n      \n      \n      \n      \n      \n    \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25:\"Grid Hardware Maintenance\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1623:\"\n<p><small>Sep 29, 21:55 PDT</small><br><strong>Completed</strong> - This maintenance has been completed and all services on Cluster 02 are running normally.</p><p><small>Sep 29, 21:01 PDT</small><br><strong>In progress</strong> - Scheduled maintenance is currently in progress. We will provide updates as necessary.</p><p><small>Sep 29, 16:12 PDT</small><br><strong>Scheduled</strong> - We will be performing a scheduled system maintenance on Thursday, September 29, 2016 to our Grid hosting service. Here are the important details:\n<br />\n<br /><b>Who is affected?</b>\n<br />\n<br />This maintenance will affect some customers on the following servers:\n<br />\n<br />Cluster 02\n<br />\n<br />You may verify whether or not your services are being impacted by this issue by locating your Cluster and Storage Segment in your Server Guide. For more information on how to locate your Server Guide in the AccountCenter, please reference the following (mt) Community article.\n<br />\n<br />Server Guide\n<br />https://mediatemple.net/community/products/grid/204643840/server-guide\n<br />\n<br /><b>When will this maintenance happen?</b>\n<br />\n<br />This maintenance will occur between 9:00 PM and 1:00 AM PT, Thursday, September 29, 2016.\n<br />\n<br /><b>What is changing?</b>\n<br />\n<br />Consolidation of our Grid Cluster hardware.\n<br />\n<br /><b>Why is this maintenance happening?</b>\n<br />\n<br />This maintenance is happening because failure of the equipment could cause prolonged downtime. This is being done as preventative maintenance.\n<br />\n<br /><b>Symptoms:</b>\n<br />•  Inability to access web, SSH, or FTP.</p>      \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 29 Sep 2016 21:55:53 -0700\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"http://status.mediatemple.net/incidents/p3m59ghvvwz5\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"http://status.mediatemple.net/incidents/p3m59ghvvwz5\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:20;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:40:\"\n      \n      \n      \n      \n      \n    \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25:\"Grid Hardware Maintenance\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1657:\"\n<p><small>Sep 29, 21:54 PDT</small><br><strong>Completed</strong> - This maintenance has been completed and all services on Cluster 01 are running normally.</p><p><small>Sep 29, 21:01 PDT</small><br><strong>In progress</strong> - Scheduled maintenance is currently in progress. We will provide updates as necessary.</p><p><small>Sep 29, 13:43 PDT</small><br><strong>Scheduled</strong> - We will be performing a scheduled system maintenance on Thursday, September 29, 2016 to our Grid hosting service. Here are the important details:\n<br />\n<br /><b>Who is affected?</b>\n<br />\n<br />This maintenance will affect customers on the following servers:\n<br />\n<br />Cluster 01\n<br />\n<br />You may verify whether or not your services are being impacted by this issue by locating your Cluster and Storage Segment in your Server Guide. For more information on how to locate your Server Guide in the AccountCenter, please reference the following (mt) Community article.\n<br />\n<br />Server Guide\n<br />https://mediatemple.net/community/products/grid/204643840/server-guide\n<br />\n<br /><b>When will this maintenance happen?</b>\n<br />\n<br />This maintenance will occur between 9:00 PM and 1:00 AM PT, Thursday, September 29, 2016.\n<br />\n<br /><b>What is changing?</b>\n<br />\n<br />This maintenance will further optimize hardware on Clusters 01\n<br />\n<br /><b>Why is this maintenance happening?</b>\n<br />\n<br />This maintenance is happening because failure of the equipment could cause prolonged downtime. This is being done to improve security, stability, and performance.\n<br />\n<br /><b>Symptoms:</b>\n<br />•  Inability to access web, SSH, or FTP.</p>      \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 29 Sep 2016 21:54:00 -0700\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"http://status.mediatemple.net/incidents/9yq8wzsxtfnb\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"http://status.mediatemple.net/incidents/9yq8wzsxtfnb\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:21;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:40:\"\n      \n      \n      \n      \n      \n    \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:46:\"Grid Mail Node n51.mail01 Service Interruption\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1081:\"\n<p><small>Sep 28, 13:25 PDT</small><br><strong>Resolved</strong> - This incident has been resolved.</p><p><small>Sep 28, 12:23 PDT</small><br><strong>Identified</strong> - (mt) Engineers are currently working on an issue affecting Grid Mail Node n51.mail01. Affected customers may experience difficulty sending and receiving email.\n<br />\n<br />You may verify whether or not your services are being impacted by this issue by locating your Mail Node in your Server Guide. For more information on how to locate your Server Guide in the AccountCenter, please reference the following (mt) Community article.\n<br />\n<br /><a href=https://mediatemple.net/community/products/grid/204643840/\">https://mediatemple.net/community/products/grid/204643840/</a>\n<br />\n<br />We are actively working on getting this issue resolved as soon as possible. We apologize for any inconvenience this issue has caused, and we appreciate your patience while we work quickly towards a resolution.\n<br />\n<br /><b>Symptoms:</b>\n<br />•  Inability to send or receive email via IMAP, POP, or SMTP.</p>      \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 28 Sep 2016 13:25:16 -0700\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"http://status.mediatemple.net/incidents/t8q9lys1bm3k\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\