br /><a href=https://mediatemple.net/community/products/grid/204643840/\">https://mediatemple.net/community/products/grid/204643840/</a>\n<br />\n<br />We are actively working on getting this issue resolved as soon as possible. We apologize for any inconvenience this issue has caused, and we appreciate your patience while we work quickly towards a resolution.\n<br />\n<br /><b>Symptoms:</b>\n<br />•  Inability to send or receive email via IMAP, POP, or SMTP.</p>      \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 26 Sep 2016 12:31:04 -0700\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"http://status.mediatemple.net/incidents/9ppkr2548mfq\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"http://status.mediatemple.net/incidents/9ppkr2548mfq\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:24;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:40:\"\n      \n      \n      \n      \n      \n    \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:38:\"WordPress Hosting Service Interruption\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:693:\"\n<p><small>Sep 23, 10:27 PDT</small><br><strong>Resolved</strong> - (mt) Engineers have addressed the cause of the interruption, and access should be restored. Please contact support if you are still experiencing issues.</p><p><small>Sep 23, 06:45 PDT</small><br><strong>Investigating</strong> - (mt) Engineers are currently investigati